{"tid":1569051,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京一人行 幫下手度行程","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T13:18:28.000Z","uid":31602,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f0cd0ef17d1a2dcce754429604ecab0cd2c100","tid":1569051,"uid":31602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>D1 9/12 早機去 放低行李之後</strong><br />\n小石川後樂園 打下卡<br />\n秋葉原 行下<br />\n東京鐵塔 睇夜景<br />\n<br />\n<strong>D2新宿+東京 10/12</strong><br />\n下北澤站 睇古着<br />\n新宿御苑 打卡影相<br />\n大田黑公園<br />\n唔知有冇時間去埋吉祥寺<br />\n<br />\n<strong>D3台場一日遊 11/12</strong><br />\nAqua City＋DECKS購物中心<br />\nDiverCity - 睇獨角獸<br />\nteamLab Borderless 打卡<br />\n<br />\n<strong>D4鎌倉一日遊 13/12</strong><br />\n鐮倉大佛 or 長谷寺<br />\n鐮倉高校前 SLAM DUNK<br />\n去埋江之島岩屋<br />\n<br />\n其實可以去足一個星期,不過未諗到仲有咩地方好去<br />\n巴絲打可唔可以幫手諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣會唔會太鬆散/太CHUR"},{"pid":"193c8d0af288ad70ff4aec5c2e54ab41aa1e805d","tid":1569051,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"鎌倉會唔會留一日過夜<br />\n有pass可以搭吊車同電車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過景點一日都去哂"},{"pid":"11720416d4f88e363cca15777848f2426928356a","tid":1569051,"uid":31602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"193c8d0af288ad70ff4aec5c2e54ab41aa1e805d","tid":1569051,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"鎌倉會唔會留一日過夜<br />\n有pass可以搭吊車同電車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過景點一日都去哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"一日都去晒既話<br />\n有乜特別野要留一日過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見嗰到啲景點都好近 應該一日行得晒"},{"pid":"e8fbab79f6d935af82e4f933678050010436e0cf","tid":1569051,"uid":221265,"like":0,"